net.opentsdb.core

接口 iHistogramRowSeq

  • 所有超级接口:
    HistogramDataPoints, Iterable<HistogramDataPoint>
    所有已知实现类:
    HistogramRowSeq

    public interface iHistogramRowSeq
extends HistogramDataPoints
    Clone of the iRowSeq interface but for histograms.
    从以下版本开始:
    2.4

    • 嵌套类概要

      嵌套类 
      限定符和类型 接口和说明
      static interface  iHistogramRowSeq.Iterator
      An interface for an iterator that all row sequences must implement.

    • 方法详细资料

      • setRow

        void setRow(byte[] key,
            List<HistogramDataPoint> row)
        Sets the initial column in the sequence. The key cannot be empty.
        参数:
        key - The row key.
        row - A non-null list of histogram points.
        抛出:
        IllegalStateException - if setRow(byte[], List) or addRow(List) has already been called.

      • addRow

        void addRow(List<HistogramDataPoint> row)
        Adds a column in the proper sequence in the row. Must be called after setRow(byte[], List) has been called.
        参数:
        row - A non-null list of histogram points.
        抛出:
        IllegalStateException - if setRow(byte[], List) has not been called first.

      • key

        byte[] key()
        Returns the row key this sequence represents. May be null if setRow(byte[], List) has not been called.
        返回:
        The row key for this sequence.

      • baseTime

        long baseTime()
        Returns the base time for the row in Unix epoch seconds.
        返回:
        The base time for the row.
        抛出:
        NullPointerException - if setRow(byte[], List) has not been called.

      • internalIterator

        iHistogramRowSeq.Iterator internalIterator()
        返回:
        an internal iterator for this row sequence.
